For the next {c_number}{s1}{/c} minutes:
{icon:bullet} Increases Healing by {c_number}15%{/c} and Revive speed by {c_number}25%{/c}.
{icon:bullet} After Reviving a player, gain {c_number}+10%{/c} Move Speed for {c_number}5{/c} seconds.
{icon:bullet} Experience gained is increased by {c_number}8%{/c}.
